  <summary>Control your desktop with mobile gestures</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      Astra Gesture Control allows you to control your desktop computer
      using gestures from your mobile device. Turn your phone into a
      wireless mouse, keyboard, and remote control.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Wireless mouse control with adjustable sensitivity</li>
      <li>Gesture-based scrolling and clicking</li>
      <li>Virtual keyboard input from mobile device</li>
      <li>QR code for easy mobile connection</li>
      <li>Real-time activity monitoring</li>
      <li>Beautiful, modern user interface</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
